  {
   "start": 231.15,
   "end": 233.43,
   "text": "So, and same thing with the Buddhists."
  },
  {
   "start": 233.43,
   "end": 243.99,
   "text": "Anything, you know, meditation or the belief that all life is suffering, and that's what life here is about, suffering,"
